{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lesson-template-js","path":"/docker-cheatsheet","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"build-container-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#build-container-image\" aria-label=\"build container image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Build Container Image</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Build an image from the Dockerfile in the current directory and tag the image</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker build -t satyambnsal/todoapp:1.0.0 .</code></pre></div>\n<p>In ðŸ‘†command <code class=\"language-text\">satyambnsal</code> is dockerhub username and <code class=\"language-text\">1.0.0</code> is image tag.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>List all images that are locally stored with the Docker Engine</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker image ls</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Delete an image from the local image store</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker image rm satyambnsal/todoapp:1.0.0</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"share-container-image-with-others\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#share-container-image-with-others\" aria-label=\"share container image with others permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Share Container Image with Others</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Login to Dockerhub</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker login -u &lt;dockerhub-username&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Pull an image from a registry(Default registry is <a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/\">Dockerhub</a>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker pull node:14</code></pre></div>\n<p>in ðŸ‘†command, image name is <code class=\"language-text\">node</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">14</code> is image tag.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Retag a local image with a new image name and tag</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker tag satyambnsal/todoapp:1.0.0 satyambnsal/mynewtodo:2.0.0</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"run-container\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#run-container\" aria-label=\"run container permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Run Container</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Run a container from NGINX Image and expose port 3000 externally mapped to port 80 inside the container</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container run --publish 3000:80 --name nginx-server nginx</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Run ðŸ‘† container in detached mode with port mapped to 3001</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container run --publish 3001:80 --name nginx-server1 nginx</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Get Inside a running container</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container exec -it nginx-server1</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"docker-volume\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#docker-volume\" aria-label=\"docker volume permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Docker Volume</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create Docker volume</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker volume create &lt;volume-name&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Inspect docker volume</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker volume inspect &lt;volume-name|id&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Attach a volume to todoapp container</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container run --detach --publish 3006:3000 -v todoappdb:/etc/todos satyambnsal/todoapp:1.0.1</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"docker-bind-mount\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#docker-bind-mount\" aria-label=\"docker bind mount permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Docker Bind Mount</h2>\n<p>Mount current directory on host machine to NGINX server</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container run -d --name nginx-dev-server -p 80:80 -v $(pwd):/usr/share/nginx/html nginx</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"see-container-logs-and-properties\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#see-container-logs-and-properties\" aria-label=\"see container logs and properties permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>See container logs and properties</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>See container logs</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container logs &lt;container-name|container-id&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>See container logs in live mode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container logs &lt;container-name|container-id&gt; --follow</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>See container config</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container inspect &lt;container-name|container-id&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>See performance stats for all containers</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container stats</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>See list of process running inside a container</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker container top &lt;container-name|container-id&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"path":"/docker-cheatsheet","title":"Docker Cheatsheet","order":4,"section":"Docker Cheatsheet","description":""}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":1,"path":"/intro","title":"Introduction"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":2.1,"path":"/virtualization","title":"History of Virtualization"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":2.2,"path":"/containers","title":"Containers"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":2.3,"path":"/docker","title":"Docker"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":3.1,"path":"/docker-ecosystem","title":"Docker Ecosystem"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":3.2,"path":"/docker-handson","title":"Docker Handson"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":3.3,"path":"/create-docker-image","title":"How to Create Docker Image"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":4,"path":"/docker-cheatsheet","title":"Docker Cheatsheet"}}}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["2959687377"]}